name: Punks x Paris
description: CryptoPunks by Larva Labs are a collection of 24x24, 8-bit style pixel art images of misfits and eccentrics. There are 10,000 of them in existence and each one can fetch huge amounts at auction. otel heiress Paris Hilton is the latest celebrity to get fully immersed into NFT culture recently releasing her own collection with 3D designer Blake Kathryn, selling for over 1.11 Million USD. This is my homage to both these giants of the crypto art scene.
